    <description>
        <p>Yaiden is the IDE that puts the terminal in its focus, letting you focus on your work.</p>
        <p>Yaiden is still a WIP and lacks a lot of features.</p>
        <p>Clean UI: thanks to the Gtk implementation, Yaiden has a high content-to-screen ratio.</p>
        <p>Lightweight: offloads almost everything to GtkSource, keeping the implementation small.</p>
        <p>No-Annoyance: no notifications asking for your feedback or recommending you extensions.</p>
    </description>
